setup_commands: apt-get remove -y golang && apt-get install -y wget && wget https://go.dev/dl/go1.21.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz && tar -C /usr/local -xzf go1.21.5.linux-amd64.tar.gz && export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/go/bin
export PATH=/usr/local/go/bin:$PATH && go version && go test ./...
sed -i 's/go 1.23.0/go 1.21/' go.mod && go mod download && go test ./...
apt-get install -y iptables iproute2 && go test ./...
